    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Enchylea heteroducta Nielsen & Christensen, 1963. A. Anterior body region, dorsal view. Arrow: enlarged postpharyngeal ganglia on afferent fascicles with pharyngeal gland-like tissue. B. Nephridium. C. Male efferent apparatus. A – C fix." ;
